<Comment>/* ---- 5. OPERATORS -------------------------------------------------- */</Comment><br/>
<Normal Text></Normal Text><br/>
<Step>data</Step><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Constants>_null_</Constants><Normal Text>;</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  </Normal Text><Comment>/* arithmetic — * and / dont trigger comment context */</Comment><br/>
<Normal Text>  a </Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>2</Number><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Operator>**</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>3</Number><Normal Text>;</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  b </Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>15</Number><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Operator>*</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>3</Number><Normal Text>;</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  c </Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>10</Number><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Operator>/</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>4</Number><Normal Text>;</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  d </Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text> a </Normal Text><Operator>+</Operator><Normal Text> b </Normal Text><Operator>-</Operator><Normal Text> c;</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  z </Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>15</Number><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Operator>*</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>3</Number><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Operator>/</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>4</Number><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Operator>+</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>100</Number><Normal Text>;</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text></Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  </Normal Text><Comment>/* comparison — symbolic */</Comment><br/>
<Normal Text>  eq_  </Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text> (z </Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text>  </Normal Text><Number>45</Number><Normal Text>);</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  ne_  </Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text> (z </Normal Text><Operator>^=</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>45</Number><Normal Text>);</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  ne</Normal Text><Number>2</Number><Normal Text>  </Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text> (z </Normal Text><Operator>~=</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>45</Number><Normal Text>);</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  gt_  </Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text> (z </Normal Text><Operator>></Operator><Normal Text>  </Normal Text><Number>10</Number><Normal Text>);</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  lt_  </Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text> (z </Normal Text><Operator><</Operator><Normal Text>  </Normal Text><Number>200</Number><Normal Text>);</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  ge_  </Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text> (z </Normal Text><Operator>>=</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>10</Number><Normal Text>);</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  le_  </Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text> (z </Normal Text><Operator><=</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>200</Number><Normal Text>);</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  mn_  </Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text> z </Normal Text><Operator><></Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>100</Number><Normal Text>;   </Normal Text><Comment>/* min operator */</Comment><br/>
<Normal Text>  mx_  </Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text> z </Normal Text><Operator>><</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>100</Number><Normal Text>;   </Normal Text><Comment>/* max operator */</Comment><br/>
<Normal Text>  cat_ </Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><String>"a"</String><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Operator>||</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><String>"b"</String><Normal Text>; </Normal Text><Comment>/* concatenation */</Comment><br/>
<Normal Text></Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  </Normal Text><Comment>/* trailing-modifier operators */</Comment><br/>
<Normal Text>  name </Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><String>"Jones"</String><Normal Text>;</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  eq_t </Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text> (name </Normal Text><Operator>=:</Operator><Normal Text>  </Normal Text><String>"Jo"</String><Normal Text>);</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  gt_t </Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text> (name </Normal Text><Operator>>:</Operator><Normal Text>  </Normal Text><String>"Jo"</String><Normal Text>);</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  ne_t </Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text> (name </Normal Text><Operator>^=:</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><String>"Jo"</String><Normal Text>);</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text></Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  </Normal Text><Comment>/* mnemonic operators */</Comment><br/>
<Normal Text>  x </Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>5</Number><Normal Text>; y </Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>10</Number><Normal Text>;</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  </Normal Text><Control>if</Control><Normal Text> x </Normal Text><Operator>gt</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>0</Number><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Operator>and</Operator><Normal Text> y </Normal Text><Operator>lt</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>20</Number><Normal Text>  </Normal Text><Control>then</Control><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Keywords>put</Keywords><Normal Text> </Normal Text><String>"gt lt"</String><Normal Text>;</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  </Normal Text><Control>if</Control><Normal Text> x </Normal Text><Operator>ge</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>5</Number><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Operator>and</Operator><Normal Text> y </Normal Text><Operator>le</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>10</Number><Normal Text>  </Normal Text><Control>then</Control><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Keywords>put</Keywords><Normal Text> </Normal Text><String>"ge le"</String><Normal Text>;</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  </Normal Text><Control>if</Control><Normal Text> x </Normal Text><Operator>eq</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>5</Number><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Operator>or</Operator><Normal Text>  y </Normal Text><Operator>ne</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>0</Number><Normal Text>   </Normal Text><Control>then</Control><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Keywords>put</Keywords><Normal Text> </Normal Text><String>"eq ne"</String><Normal Text>;</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  </Normal Text><Control>if</Control><Normal Text> not (x </Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>0</Number><Normal Text>)         </Normal Text><Control>then</Control><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Keywords>put</Keywords><Normal Text> </Normal Text><String>"not"</String><Normal Text>;</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  </Normal Text><Control>if</Control><Normal Text> x in (</Normal Text><Number>1</Number><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>2</Number><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>3</Number><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>4</Number><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>5</Number><Normal Text>)    </Normal Text><Control>then</Control><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Keywords>put</Keywords><Normal Text> </Normal Text><String>"in"</String><Normal Text>;</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  </Normal Text><Control>if</Control><Normal Text> name </Normal Text><Operator>like</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><String>"Jo%"</String><Normal Text>     </Normal Text><Control>then</Control><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Keywords>put</Keywords><Normal Text> </Normal Text><String>"like"</String><Normal Text>;</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  </Normal Text><Control>if</Control><Normal Text> name </Normal Text><Operator>contains</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><String>"ohn"</String><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Control>then</Control><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Keywords>put</Keywords><Normal Text> </Normal Text><String>"contains"</String><Normal Text>;</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  </Normal Text><Control>if</Control><Normal Text> x </Normal Text><Operator>between</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>1</Number><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Operator>and</Operator><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Number>10</Number><Normal Text>  </Normal Text><Control>then</Control><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Keywords>put</Keywords><Normal Text> </Normal Text><String>"between"</String><Normal Text>;</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  </Normal Text><Control>if</Control><Normal Text> x </Normal Text><Operator>is</Operator><Normal Text> missing        </Normal Text><Control>then</Control><Normal Text> </Normal Text><Keywords>put</Keywords><Normal Text> </Normal Text><String>"missing"</String><Normal Text>;</Normal Text><br/>
<Step>run;</Step><br/>
<Normal Text></Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text></Normal Text><br/>
