<Comment>/* ---- 16. MISC PROCS ------------------------------------------------ */</Comment><br/>
<Normal Text></Normal Text><br/>
<Step>proc mixed</Step><Normal Text> </Normal Text><SecKeyword>data</SecKeyword><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text>sashelp.class;</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  </Normal Text><SecKeyword>class</SecKeyword><Normal Text> sex;</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  </Normal Text><SecKeyword>model</SecKeyword><Normal Text> height </Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text> age sex </Normal Text><Operator>/</Operator><Normal Text> solution ddfm</Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text>kr;</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  </Normal Text><SecKeyword>random</SecKeyword><Normal Text> intercept </Normal Text><Operator>/</Operator><Normal Text> subject</Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text>name type</Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text>un;</Normal Text><br/>
<Normal Text>  </Normal Text><SecKeyword>lsmeans</SecKeyword><Normal Text> sex </Normal Text><Operator>/</Operator><Normal Text> pdiff adjust</Normal Text><Operator>=</Operator><Normal Text>tukey;</Normal Text><br/>
